title: Biden's indecision fuels doubts he could still run in 2016
text:
> Political Biden's indecision fuels doubts he could still run in 2016 FILE - In this Sept. 16, 2015 file photo, Vice President Joe Biden speaks in Anaheim, Calif. Biden’s summer of uncertainty is turning into a fall of indecision, creating doubts about whether he could still be a serious candidate for president in 2016.
